CREATE TABLE `baiduzhidao` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `title` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `keyword` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `question` longtext,
  `best_answer` longtext,
  `best_name` longtext,
  `best_date` longtext,
  `answers` longtext,
  `second_questions` longtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;


===========linux=========
①配置环境  https://www.jianshu.com/p/26ef8a3efd19
②在linux系统上运行爬虫时报错，应考虑关闭所有的firefox进程 ps -ef|grep firefox






